{"tid":265212,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"真係咪撚返所謂'慈善機構'既壽款大使","createTime":"2017-05-31T12:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T08:10:53.000Z","uid":13474,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1c121f3ce11b4bba42a891190b9a8673cd7d3b","tid":265212,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC開post<br />\n是咁的<br />\n有間濕鳩公司想大家小心<br />\n間公司係上環同中環中間,叫Appc_<br />\n依排Sem break 想搵pt<br />\n經朋友介紹咪試下去in<br />\n普通in完話要再second in<br />\n點知所謂second in去到先知原來係training <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個training翻九半到大約三點<br />\n依一日係冇人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個到大約有十個人到<br />\n個個走前都要填晒個人資料<br />\n以為咁就in得成咗？請晒咁多人？<br />\n點知第二日翻9點就又係training<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗幾時簽約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又冇講幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係話開到一張單會有幾錢<br />\n最高大約有$5xx一張<br />\n終於到簽約喇<br />\n以為唔洗跑數，點知每條team都要追數<br />\n睇下人工點啦，竟然係冇底薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要開到單先有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢set左一個月quota最少要開幾多張單<br />\n過左指定quota再加錢<br />\n仲話想走可以即日通知，串撚到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣發覺真係中左伏<br />\n間公司係接左UNICE__聯合國兒__基金會做<br />\n上午有人教點stop人sell佢講到好專業咁<br />\n下午就要去指定地方做野，仲要冇車錢俾claim<br />\n慈善機構搵人追數追佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗平時食水都好撚深下<br />\n大家有機會撞到食間公司既小心D"},{"pid":"1b2545db511aae8a416eb6d6d54f8b9bee0b5bcb","tid":265212,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5465159f3a9a329dcad548ff90593902a25300a","tid":265212,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201